{"tid":1336254,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"成語故事-破釜沉舟","createTime":"2019-07-21T00:44:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-21T00:46:15.000Z","uid":48623,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"c609099d44d67795f37f714dff6ad604bda4b8ba","tid":1336254,"uid":48623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T00:44:03.000Z","msg":"秦朝末年，秦國大將章邯攻打趙國，把巨鹿城包圍住。楚國的楚懷王派項羽救援趙國。項羽就帶領部隊去救巨鹿。當部隊渡過漳河以后，項羽命令把所有的船隻都鑿破，沉到河底下去，再把飯鍋完全打碎，把岸上的房屋全部燒光，每個人都只發三天的乾糧。他這樣是向大家表示，寧願戰死也不後退的決心。結果，項羽的軍隊受到激勵，士氣高漲，經過九次激烈戰斗，終于殲滅了秦國軍隊，項羽也因此成為當時各處諸侯的領袖。<br />\n<br />\n成語造句<br />\n<br />\n大家要抱著「破釜沈舟」的精神，堅持到最後一秒鐘，絕不放棄。<br />\n<br />\n事到如今，我們也只有「破釜沉舟」，拚死一戰，以求生路了。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc779913019f58c2033de57a866280f43713f034","tid":1336254,"uid":48623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T00:44:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e2eb142ff6a9e7eb49036698fba33eb13f5f3728","tid":1336254,"uid":48623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T00:45:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23d4c8f1adcc2878bd1d8f7a974d9ac1c1901cae","tid":1336254,"uid":48623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T00:46:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}